\u2013 production {{small|(tracks 3-4, 10)}}\n* Kid Culture \u2013 production {{small|(tracks 5, 9, 17 (bonus))}}\n* HARV \u2013 production {{small|(tracks 6-7, 16)}}\n* [[JaVale McGee|JaVale 'Pierre' McGee]] \u2013 production {{small|(track 6)}}\n* [[Louis Bell]] \u2013 Post Malone vocal production {{small|(track 7)}}\n* [[Vinylz]] \u2013 production {{small|(track 11)}}\n* [[Boi-1da]] \u2013 production {{small|(track 11)}}\n* CVRE \u2013 production {{small|(track 11)}}\n* Jahaan Sweet \u2013 co-production {{small|(track 11)}}\n* Phil Beaudreau \u2013 production {{small|(track 12)}}\n* Tom Strahle \u2013 production {{small|(track 12)}}\n* Nasri Atweh \u2013 production {{small|(track 13)}}\n* [[Adam Messinger]] \u2013 production {{small|(track 13)}}\n* Sons of Sonix \u2013 production {{small|(track 14)}}\n* Joshua Williams \u2013 production {{small|(track 16)}}\n{{div col end}}\n\n===Technical===\n{{div col}}\n* Josh Gudwin \u2013 engineering, mixing {{small|(all tracks)}}\n* [[Chris O'Ryan|Chris 'Tek' O'Ryan]] \u2013 engineering {{small|(all tracks)}}\n* Chenao Wang \u2013 assistant engineer {{small|(tracks 1-3, 5, 7, 12-13, 15, 17(bonus))}}\n* Kory Welty \u2013 engineering {{small|(track 2)}}\n* Elijah Marrett-Hitch \u2013 mixing assistant {{small|(tracks 5, 17(bonus))}}\n* Louis Bell \u2013 recording {{small|(track 7)}}\n* [[David Burd]] \u2013 vocals recording {{small|(track 8)}}\n* Mark Parsift \u2013 Kehlani vocals recording {{small|(track 11)}} \n* Phil Beaudreau \u2013 engineering {{small|(track 12)}}\n* Summer Walker \u2013 vocals recording {{small|(track 17(bonus))}}\n* Kendall Roark Bailey \u2013 vocals recording, mixing {{small|(track 17(bonus))}}\n{{div col end}}\n\n===Artwork===\n{{div col}}\n* Jessica Severn \u2013 design and packaging\n* Chris Shelley \u2013 design and packaging\n* Joe Termini \u2013 [[photography]]\n* Jennifer Beal \u2013 package production\n* Andy Proctor \u2013 package production\n{{div col\u3000end}}\n\n==Charts==\n{| class=\"wiki