nd [[Timbaland|Timothy Mosley]], as performed by [[dvsn]].\n\n==Personnel==\nCredits adapted from [[AllMusic]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.allmusic.com/album/changes-mw0003352549|title=Changes \u2013 Justin Bieber {{!}} Credits|publisher=AllMusic|accessdate=March 19, 2020}}</ref>\n\n===Performers and vocals===\n{{div col}}\n* [[Justin Bieber]] \u2013 vocals {{small|(all tracks)}}\n* [[Quavo]] \u2013 vocals {{small|(track 4)}}\n* [[Post Malone]] \u2013 vocals {{small|(track 7)}}\n* [[Clever (rapper)|Clever]] \u2013 vocals {{small|(track 7)}}\n* [[Lil Dicky]] \u2013 vocals {{small|(track 8)}}\n* [[Travis Scott]] \u2013 vocals {{small|(track 10)}}\n* [[Kehlani]] \u2013 vocals {{small|(track 11)}}\n* [[Summer Walker]] \u2013 vocals {{small|(track 17)(bonus)}}\n* [[Poo Bear|Jason 'Poo Bear' Boyd]] \u2013 background vocals {{small|(tracks 2\u20134, 6)}}\n* [[Sasha Sirota]] \u2013 guitar {{small|(tracks 1, 15)}}\n* [[Tainy|Marco 'Tainy' Mas\u00eds]] \u2013 drums, keyboards, bass {{small|(track 2)}}\n* [[Bernard \"Harv\" Harvey|Bernard Harvey]] \u2013 keyboards {{small|(tracks 7, 16)}}, bass {{small|(track 16)}}\n* Daniel Hackett \u2013 keyboards {{small|(track 9)}}\n* Jun Ha Kim \u2013 bass, keyboards, guitar {{small|(track 11)}}\n* Phil Beaudreau \u2013 drum programming, bass, keyboards, background vocals {{small|(track 12)}}\n* Tom Strahle \u2013 guitar {{small|(track 12)}}\n* [[Nasri Atweh]] \u2013 guitar {{small|(track 13)}}\n* Moses Samuels \u2013 keyboards {{small|(track 14)}}\n{{div col end}}\n\n===Production===\n{{div col}}\n* Justin Bieber \u2013 executive production\n* [[Scooter Braun]] \u2013 executive production\n* Jason 'Poo Bear' Boyd \u2013 co-executive production, production {{small|(all tracks)}}, vocal production {{small|(track 11)}}\n* Josh Gudwin \u2013 co-executive production, production {{small|(track 2, 11)}}, vocal production {{small|(all tracks)}}\n* Sasha Sirota \u2013 production {{small|(tracks 1, 5, 15, 17 (bonus))}}\n* Marco 'Tainy' Mas\u00eds \u2013 production {{small|(track 2)}}\n* [[The Audibles]] \u2013 production {{small|(tracks 3-4, 10)}}\n* Kid Culture \u2013 production {{small|(tracks 5, 9, 17 (bonus))}}\n* HARV \u2013 production {{small|(tracks 6-7, 16)}}\n* [[JaVale McGee|JaVale 'Pierre' McGee]] \u2013 production {{small|(track 6)}}\n* [[Louis Bell]] \u2013 Post Malone vocal production {{small|(track 7)}}\n* [[Vinylz]] \u2013 production {{small|(track 11)}}\n* [[Boi-1da]] \u2013 production {{small|(track 11)}}\n* CVRE \u2013 production {{small|(track 11)}}\n* Jahaan Sweet \u2013 co-production {{small|(track 11)}}\n* Phil Beaudreau \u2013 production {{small|(track 12)}}\n* Tom Strahle \u2013 production {{small|(track 12)}}\n* Nasri Atweh \u2013 production {{small|(track 13)}}\n* [[Adam Messinger]] \u2013 production {{small|(track 13)}}\n* Sons of Sonix \u2013 production {{small|(track 14)}}\n* Joshua Williams \u2013 production {{small|(track 16)}}\n{{div col end}}\n\n===Technical===\n{{div col}}\n* Josh Gudwin \u2013 engineering, mixing {{small|(all tracks)}}\n* [[Chris O'Ryan|Chris 'Tek' O'Ryan]] \u2013 engineering {{small|(all tracks)}}\n* Chenao Wang \u2013 assistant engineer {{small|(tracks 1-3, 5, 7, 12-13, 15, 17(bonus))}}\n* Kory Welty \u2013 engineering {{small|(track 2)}}\n* Elijah Marrett-Hitch \u2013 mixing assistant {{small|(tracks 5, 17(bonus))}}\n* Louis Bell \u2013 recording {{small|(track 7)}}\n* [[David Burd]] \u2013 vocals recording {{small|(track 8)}}\n* Mark Parsift \u2013 Kehlani vocals recording {{small|(track 11)}} \n* Phil Beaudreau \u2013 engineering {{small|(track 12)}}\n* Summer Walker \u2013 vocals recording {{small|(track 17(bonus))}}\n* Kendall Roark Bailey \u2013 vocals recording, mixing {{small|(track 17(bonus))}}\n{{div col end}}\n\n===Artwork===\n{{div col}}\n* Jessica Severn \u2013 design and packaging\n* Chris Shelley \u2013 design and packaging\n* Joe Termini \u2013 [[photography]]\n* Jennifer Beal \u2013 package production\n* Andy Proctor \u2013 package production\n{{div col\u3000end}}\n\n==Charts==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2020)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br />position\n|-\n{{album chart|Australia|2|artist=Justin Bieber|album=Changes|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 22, 2020}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Austria|2|artist=Justin Bieber|album=Changes|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 27, 2020}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Flanders|3|artist=Justin Bieber|album=Changes|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 22, 2020}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Wallonia|5|artist=Justin Bieber|album=Changes|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 22, 2020}}\n|-\n{{album chart|BillboardCanada|1|artist=Justin Bieber|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 24, 2020}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Czech|1|date=202008|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 25, 2020}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Denmark|3|artist=Justin Bieber|album=Changes|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 26, 2020}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Netherlands|1|artist=Justin Bieber|album=Changes|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 22, 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Estonian Albums (''[[Eesti Ekspress]]'')<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ekspress.delfi.ee/areen/eesti-tipp-40-muusikas-eesti-laulu-lood-tungivad-edetabelisse-kes-koige-korgemale?id=89041723|title=ALBUMID TIPP-40|work=[[Eesti Ekspress]]|date=February 25, 2020|accessdate=February 26, 2020}}</ref>\n| 1\n|-\n{{album chart|Finland|5|artist=Justin Bieber|album=Changes|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 23, 2020}}\n|-\n{{album chart|France|9|artist=Justin Bieber|album=Changes|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 24, 2020}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Germany4|4|id=400920|artist=Justin Bieber|album=Changes|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 21, 2020}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Hungary|34|year=2020|week=8|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 28, 2020}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Ireland3|2|date=20200221|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 22, 2020}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Italy|7|artist=Justin Bieber|album=Changes|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 22, 2020}